Agar maqsad **[https://gershon.vercel.app/](https://gershon.vercel.app/)** ga o‘xshash bo‘lsa, unda ortiqcha 3D pizza uchirishlar kerak emas. Sayt premium, minimalist, qorong‘i fonli, katta tipografiya va smooth animatsiyalar bilan bo‘lishi kerak.

Kiro uchun quyidagi promptni ber:

---

# ALIYA ABI PREMIUM WEBSITE

Create a premium restaurant website for "Aliya Abi" located in Termiz, Uzbekistan.

The website style should be heavily inspired by the visual quality, layout structure, typography hierarchy, animations and storytelling approach of Gershon.vercel.app.

DO NOT create a typical restaurant website.

The feeling should be:

* Modern
* Elegant
* Premium
* Dark luxury
* Cinematic
* Minimalistic
* Expensive

Tech Stack:

* Next.js 15
* TypeScript
* TailwindCSS
* Framer Motion
* Theatre.js
* Anime.js
* GSAP
* Lenis Smooth Scroll
* Spline (light usage)
* Three.js (subtle effects only)

---

