# GLOBAL STYLE

Large typography.

Very large section spacing.

Luxury restaurant branding.

Every section should breathe.

Nothing should feel crowded.

Use smooth reveal animations.

Use subtle parallax.

No bright colors.

No excessive effects.

Everything should feel premium.

