# ANIMATION RULES

Use Framer Motion everywhere.

Fade Up

Scale In

Slide Reveal

Text Reveal

Parallax

Image Zoom

Smooth Hover

No aggressive animations.

No bouncing.

No flashy effects.

Animations should feel elegant.

---

# RESPONSIVE

Mobile-first.

Perfect tablet support.

Perfect desktop support.

Maintain luxury feeling on all devices.

---

# IMPORTANT

The final result must feel almost identical in quality and atmosphere to Gershon.vercel.app, but redesigned completely for Aliya Abi restaurant branding, food content, colors and identity.

Focus on typography, spacing, imagery and smooth animations more than heavy 3D effects.

The goal is to make visitors think:
"this restaurant looks premium before I even see the menu."
